author: jdonnerstag
msg: Few changes to MarkupParser et al.
- Rename MarkupParser to AbstractMarkupParser and removed all Wicket specific stuff
- MarkupParser now extends from AbstractMarkupParser and configures the parser with Wicket specific filters
- changed awkward naming of get/setParent() in IMarkupFilter to get/setNextFilter()
- add a means to configure Wicket's default filters during initialization and allows to disable filters. See MarkupFactory
